        // T√≠nh gi·ªù k·∫øt th√∫c d·ª±a v√†o th·ªùi l∆∞·ª£ng phim & gi·ªù b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu
        function calculateEndTime() {
            const movieSelect = document.getElementById('movieSelect');
            const startTimeInput = document.getElementById('startTime');
            const endTimeInput = document.getElementById('endTime');

            if (!movieSelect || !startTimeInput || !endTimeInput) return;

            const duration = parseInt(movieSelect.selectedOptions[0]?.dataset.duration || '0');
            const startVal = startTimeInput.value;
            if (!startVal) return;
            if (!duration) {
                showNotification('Phim ch∆∞a c√≥ th·ªùi l∆∞·ª£ng n√™n kh√¥ng t√≠nh ƒë∆∞·ª£c gi·ªù k·∫øt th√∫c', 'warning');
                return;
            }

            const [h, m] = startVal.split(':').map(Number);
            if (isNaN(h) || isNaN(m)) return;

            const startDate = new Date();
            startDate.setHours(h, m, 0, 0);
            const endDate = new Date(startDate.getTime() + duration * 60000);

            const endHours = String(endDate.getHours()).padStart(2, '0');
            const endMinutes = String(endDate.getMinutes()).padStart(2, '0');
            endTimeInput.value = `${endHours}:${endMinutes}`;
        }

